{"name":"Captain Charon","size":"medium","type":"Humanoid","tag":"","alignment":"neutral good","hitDice":"9","armorName":"studded leather","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":1,"otherArmorDesc":"12","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"20","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"20","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"60 (8d10 + 16)","speedDesc":"80 ft. mounted, 30 ft standing.","strPoints":"10","dexPoints":"18","conPoints":"13","intPoints":"15","wisPoints":"17","chaPoints":"9","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"7","customCr":"2 (450 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":true,"legendariesDescription":"","isLair":true,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside aboard the _Thetis_, [MON] commands the crew of the _Thetis_. [MON] gains one crew action which they can use only at the end of another creature's turn. [MON] regains spent crew actions at the start of its turn.","lairDescriptionEnd":"At full strength, the _Thetis_ has 15 crew members with the following stats in-combat: AC 13, HP 25. (+3 to checks/saves).\n\n_Actions:_\n\n> Shortsword: _Melee weapon attack_ +5 to hit, [1d6+3] slashing damage\n> Rifle: _Ranged weapon attack_ +5 to hit, [3d6] piercing damage","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the centaur's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the centaur's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the centaur dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"[MON] makes two attacks, one with their Sun-Dappled Scimitar and one with their whip."},{"name":"Sun-Dappled Scimitar","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D6] slashing damage plus [1D6] radiant damage. The target must succeed a DC [WIS SAVE] constitution save or be blinded for 1 minute (or until it saves at the end of its turn). Once a creature saves it is immune for 24 hours."},{"name":"Whip","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [DEX ATK] to hit, reach 15 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [DEX 1D4] slashing damage. The target must succeed on a DC [DEX SAVE] strength saving throw or be moved 5 ft."}],"bonusActions":[{"name":"Lightfooted","desc":"[MON] can dash or disengage."}],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[{"name":"Battle Stations!","desc":"**Round One:** Each crew member can  move its speed and take the dodge action."},{"name":"Taking Maneuver","desc":"**Round Two:** Each non-crew creature aboard the ship must make a DC 12 strength saving throw or be moved 20ft in a direction, possibly falling off the ship."},{"name":"Fire!","desc":"**Round Three+:** each crew member can make a ranged attack roll at a target of [MON]'s choice."}],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[{"name":"acrobatics","stat":"dex"},{"name":"athletics","stat":"str"},{"name":"perception","stat":"wis"},{"name":"persuasion","stat":"cha"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[{"name":"Common","speaks":true}],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"The Captain","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":7,"damage":[]}